            <title>[DERBY-2423] Embedded and client differ on ResultSetMetaData.isCurrency() value for DECIMAL and  NUMERIC columns</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-2423</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Embedded returns true for ResultSetMetaData.isCurrency() for DECIMAL and NUMERIC columns. Client returns false.   I tend to think client is right here but am not sure.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
